Pakistan Demographic and Health Survey 2017-18 Fieldworker Questionnaire Data

Source: R/PKFW71.R
PKFW71.Rd

PKFW71 data of Fieldworker Questionnaire from Pakistan Demographic and Health Survey 2017-18.

FW101

Fieldworker code

FW000

Country code and phase

FW102

Fieldworker region of residence

FW103

Fieldworker type of place of residence

FW104

Fieldworker age

FW105

Fieldworker sex

FW106

Fieldworker marital status

FW107

Fieldworker number of living children

FW108

Fieldworker ever had a child who died

FW109

NA- Highest level of school attended by fieldworker

FW110

Highest grade/form/year at that level completed by fieldworker

FW111

Fieldworker religion

FW112

Fieldworker ethnicity

FW113A

English

FW113B

Urdu

FW113C

Sindhi

FW113D

Punjabi

FW113E

Sariaki

FW113F

Baluchi

FW113G

Pashto

FW113X

Other language

FW114

Fieldworker's mother tongue/native language

FW115

Has fieldworker ever worked on a DHS

FW116

Has fieldworker ever worked on any other survey

FW117

Was fieldworker working for NIPS at the time employed for DHS

FW118

Is fieldworker a permanent or temporary employee of agency

References

  1. National Institute of Population Studies (NIPS), Pakistan (http://nips.org.pk/Home.htm).
